snippet.title: TILL THE DUST SETTLES - Nigerian Movies 2025 Latest Full Movies
snippet.description:
A gripping tale of love, class, and betrayal. When Ejiro, a street-smart and fiercely independent woman, crosses paths with Ebuka, a wealthy banker, their worlds collide in an unexpected romance that defies social boundaries.

But what begins as a whirlwind love story quickly spirals into a battle for power and acceptance, as Ejiro finds herself up against Ebuka’s hostile family—and a web of secrets that threaten to destroy everything she's fought for.

Blending romance, suspense, and family intrigue, this is a story about a woman’s fight to hold on to love, identity, and truth in a world that wants to silence her.

snippet.title: THE PERFECT LIE - Nigerian Movies 2025 Latest Full Movies
snippet.description:
In the chaos of Lagos house-hunting, fiercely independent lawyer Alero and tech-savvy Kunle — once school rivals — are forced to pose as a married couple to land their dream house.

What starts as a harmless lie to beat a biased rental system turns into a hilariously messy living situation filled with fridge rules, fake wedding photos, nosy neighbors, and sparks they didn’t expect.

But when pretending starts to feel real, they must face the question:
Can a relationship built on a lie survive the truth?
